Package com.intellij.psi.codeStyle

Class MinusculeMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.psi.codeStyle.MinusculeMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NameUtil.Matcher, Matcher
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AllOccurrencesMatcher, FixingLayoutMatcher, PreferStartMatchMatcherWrapper

    public abstract class MinusculeMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements Matcher
    Tells whether a string matches a specific pattern. Allows for lowercase camel-hump matching. Used in navigation, code completion, speed search etc.
    See Also:
    Inheritors MUST override `matchingFragments` and `matchingDegree` methods, they are not abstract for binary compatibility.
